data.description: Welcome to 2213 Minnie St. This cozy four bedroom, one and a half bath ranch is ready to host its new family. Sellers have added all new duct work, a whole house generator hookup, privacy fence with a doggy door on the back door of the home for your four-legged family members, appliances in 2021, and the roof and furnace were new when they bought the home. The pool has a new sand filter and all equipment stays with the house for summer fun for years to come. Attention to detail for convenience the lights are all smart set up to be synced to your Alexa. Close to shops and highways 2213 Minnie st is waitIng for its new owners.  Measurements are estimates, buyer/buyers agent to verify all information
